des:
Bimar-Live Smart products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your plug and air purifier.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your plug and air purifier - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your Bimar-Live Smart products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Bimar-Live Smart" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "Bimar-Live Smart" app;
(3). You need to have some Bimar-Live Smart devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Bimar-Live Smart" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Bimar Live Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Bimar Live Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Bimar Live Smart", and you'll be navigated to "Bimar Live Smart" login page;
(9). Open "Bimar-Live Smart" App, click More Service, choose "Alexa". Link with Verification Code, copy the Code, put code into the login page；
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom plug.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom plug.”
“Alexa, turn on air purifier.”
“Alexa, turn off air purifier.”
